  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u3-s1",
      "text": "I put down Charlie and the Chocolate Factory.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p1"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s2",
      "text": "But I kept going over the exciting story in my mind.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p1"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s3",
      "text": "The book was full of magic.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p1"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s4",
      "text": "But Charlie's happy family was the most magical part of the story.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p1"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s5",
      "text": "Charlie's home was a small house at the side of a big town.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p2"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s6",
      "text": "His family was very poor.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p2"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s7",
      "text": "His four grandparents stayed in the only bed in the house.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p2"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s8",
      "text": "The family never had enough food.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p2"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s9",
      "text": "They always ate watery cabbage soup for dinner.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p2"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s10",
      "text": "In winter, the freezing wind swept across the floor all night long.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s11",
      "text": "To my surprise, the family were happy together.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s12",
      "text": "In the evenings, Charlie sat with his grandparents in bed and listened to their stories.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s13",
      "text": "Charlie's parents often joined in.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s14",
      "text": "Every night, the room became a happy place.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p4"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s15",
      "text": "The whole family forgot about their hungry and poor life.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p4"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s16",
      "text": "This touched me greatly.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p4"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s17",
      "text": "In some people's minds, happiness comes from things like money.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p4"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s18",
      "text": "But love, in fact, is the key to happiness.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p4"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-s19",
      "text": "Oscar Wilde once said, \"Keep love in your heart. A life without it is like a sunless garden...\" There are so many reasons to be happy. I think love is the most important one. It can move us, change us and give us a life full of happiness.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-p4"
    }
  ],
